text.__SUMMARY__: Albizia carrii is a species of legume in the family Fabaceae. It is found only in Papua New Guinea.
text.References: World Conservation Monitoring Centre (1998). "Albizia carrii". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T37566A10064248. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T37566A10064248.en. Retrieved 18 December 2017.
